          "name": "Connect MCP server",
          "fill": "#ffffffff",
          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
          "width": 1597,
          "content": "Go to Terminal and run claude code:`claude`\n\nType /mcp\n\nIt should list pencil MCP tools.\n\nNow ask Claude \nGenerate code from \"Step 3 Frame\" (or simply from the selected frame)\n\nPro tip: You can also generate designs from within the terminal, this will give you access to more files in the repo",
          "lineHeight": 1.399999976158142,
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "fontSize": 36,
          "fontWeight": "normal"
        }
      ]
    },
